title: Virtual Pool 3 DL (Version 3311)
description:
Not a new game but far better than any other pool/snooker sim including the newly released and awefull WSC "real" 2009.

Great touch control with mouse movements controlling the cue action directly.
Play online using GameSpy Arcade with this version! Note that all old CD version are not compatable with this version so don't waste your time downloading those! (if it's not 73mb then its not good)

File includes patch, copy it to install directory.
